        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{(p,q)\\in\\N^2}\\frac1{a^p+b^q}\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\({a&gt;1,b&gt;1}\\)</span>.</p>\n"
